original: Lange, Sven Rudolf, assuransdirek-tör, Göteborg, f. 22/7/Ö6 i Gbg av assu-ransdir. Einar L. o. Agnes Virginia Zetterström. G. m. Ingvor Ström. Barn: Hans Einar Rudolf f. 33, Bo Georg 34, Ann Agnes o. Gun Margareta 39. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 25, jur. kansliex. i Upps. 28. Anst. v. Sv. Angf. Assuransfören. i Gbg 29-40, verkst. dir. i Öms. Försäkr :bol. Pro-tection o. Indemnity i Gbg 41-46, dito i Försäkr :bol. Atlantica i Gbg sed. 46. Ordf. i styr. f. Majornas Pantlåne A-B i Gbg sed. 43, kassadir. i Sjömanna Sällskapet i Gbg sed. 43. Medl. av SFMK (GFMF) sed. 38.
translated: Lange, Sven Rudolf, insurance director, Gothenburg, born on July 22, 1906 in Gothenburg, son of insurance director Einar L. and Agnes Virginia Zetterström. Married to Ingvor Ström. Children: Hans Einar Rudolf born in 1933, Bo Georg in 1934, Ann Agnes and Gun Margareta in 1939. Completed high school in Gothenburg in 1925, legal clerk exam in Uppsala in 1928. Employed by Swedish Marine Insurance Association in Gothenburg from 1929 to 1940, executive director of Protection and Indemnity Mutual Insurance Company in Gothenburg from 1941 to 1946, and the same position in Atlantica Mutual Insurance Company in Gothenburg since 1946. Chairman of the board for Majornas Pawnshop A-B in Gothenburg since 1943, cashier of the Seaman's Society in Gothenburg since 1943. Member of the Swedish Society for Sea Rescue (SFMK) since 1938.
